Insider Activity


Individual




Alton F. Doody



Mr. Alton F. Doody, III, is Chairman at Bravo Brio Restaurant Group, Inc., a Member at Young Presidents' Organization, Inc., and a Member at International Council of Shopping Centers, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Cleveland Area Restaurant Association.
Mr. Doody was previously employed as Founder by Lindey's German Village. He also served on the board at Newell Rubbermaid, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from Ohio Wesleyan University and a graduate degree from Cornell University.



