Bravo Brio Restaurant Group, Inc. (BBRG) Posts Quarterly Earnings Results, Beats Expectations By $0.03 EPS

Bravo Brio Restaurant Group, Inc. (NASDAQ:BBRG) posted its earnings results on Tuesday. The company reported $0.12 earnings per share for the quarter, beating the Thomson Reuters’ consensus estimate of $0.09 by $0.03. Bravo Brio Restaurant Group had a positive return on equity of 8.07% and a negative net margin of 0.98%. The business earned $101.70 million during the quarter, compared to the consensus estimate of $101.61 million. During the same period in the previous year, the business earned $0.23 EPS. The business’s quarterly revenue was down 5.2% on a year-over-year basis. .....

